Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.32,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1\fs48}本字幕由 今晚月色真美 个人制作\N{\fs42}仅供练习使用 请勿用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.32,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(960,840)}庇护所.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,JP,,0,0,0,,Text-JP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:06.24,JP,,0,0,0,,この先に　何があるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.46,JP,,0,0,0,,いつからか　考えなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:17.96,JP,,0,0,0,,考え方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.56,JP,,0,0,0,,それすら忘れてしまったのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.44,JP,,0,0,0,,変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:36.32,JP,,0,0,0,,自分だけの世界が　毎日が　続いていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.02,JP,,0,0,0,,でも　寂しくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:42.84,JP,,0,0,0,,どうってことないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.62,JP,,0,0,0,,思い出が悲しいことだったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.18,JP,,0,0,0,,信じて進んでいくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.34,JP,,0,0,0,,寂しさを知ってしまって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.78,JP,,0,0,0,,くじけそうになっても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:16.98,JP,,0,0,0,,あなたのおかげで　思い出して　強くなれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.72,JP,,0,0,0,,ひとりじゃないって　あなたのおかげで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.30,JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,Text-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:06.24,CN,,0,0,0,,在这前方会有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.46,CN,,0,0,0,,不知从何时开始  我停止了思考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:17.96,CN,,0,0,0,,就连思考的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.56,CN,,0,0,0,,或许也都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.44,CN,,0,0,0,,一成不变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:36.32,CN,,0,0,0,,日复一日地过着独自一人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.02,CN,,0,0,0,,可是  我不觉得孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:42.84,CN,,0,0,0,,也不觉得有什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.62,CN,,0,0,0,,即使这些回忆让我悲伤难过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.18,CN,,0,0,0,,但我会带着信念向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.34,CN,,0,0,0,,哪怕会寂寞沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.78,CN,,0,0,0,,哪怕看不到希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:16.98,CN,,0,0,0,,但多亏了你  我才回想起一切  变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.72,CN,,0,0,0,,多亏了你  我才发觉自己并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.30,CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,LEC-EN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:33.63,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I could never find the right way to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:37.30,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Have you noticed I've been gone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:43.46,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}'Cause I left behind the home that you made me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:46.66,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But I will carry it along
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:50.10,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's a long way forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.98,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:56.88,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll give them shelter like you've done for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:00.38,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And I know, I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.89,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'll be watching over us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.93,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Until you're gone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:50.70,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}When I'm older I'll be silent beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:54.23,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I know words won't be enough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:03:00.32,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And they won't need to know our names or our faces
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.73,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But they will carry on for us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.92,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's a long way forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.83,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:13.63,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll give them shelter like you've done for me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.44,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And I know, I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.99,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'll be watching over us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.41,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Until you're gone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.63,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And it's a long way forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.63,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:30.44,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll give them shelter like you've done for me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:34.30,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And I know, I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.64,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'll be watching over us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.92,LRC-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Until...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,LEC-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:33.63,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我一直找不到合适的方式告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:37.30,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可曾注意到我已离开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:43.46,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我离开了你为我建造的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:46.66,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便如此 我也会独自一人前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:50.10,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}前路漫漫无期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.98,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:56.88,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会给予他们庇护 就像曾经保护我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:00.38,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我知道 我并不是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.89,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你会一直守护着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.93,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直到你离去之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:50.70,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当我老去之时 我会默默地守护在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:54.23,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我知道这些话语还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:03:00.32,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们不需要知道我们的名字和面容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.73,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但他们会为了我们继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.92,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}前路漫漫无期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.83,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:13.63,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会给予他们庇护 就像曾经保护我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.44,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我知道 我并不是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.99,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你会一直守护着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.41,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直到你离去之时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.63,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}前路漫漫无期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.63,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:30.44,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会给予他们庇护 就像曾经保护我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:34.30,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我知道 我并不是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.64,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你会一直守护着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.92,LRC-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直到…
